Package: libtemplate-plugin-clickable-email-perl
Version: 0.01-2
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Debian Perl Group <pkg-perl-maintainers@lists.alioth.debian.org>
Installed-Size: 25
Depends: perl, libemail-find-perl, libtemplate-perl
Section: perl
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://metacpan.org/release/Template-Plugin-Clickable-Email
Description: plugin to make clickable e-mail addresses with Template Toolkit
 Template::Plugin::Clickable::Email is a plugin for Template Toolkit that
 converts any e-mail addresses found in the filtered text into proper
 HTML mailto: links.
